                                                                                      Position Management    Job Management
Ability to report on open and filled positions                                               Yes                 No
Assign default orgs(company, cost center etc..) to unfilled positions                        Yes                 No
Allow compensation defaulting                                                                Yes                 Yes
Track position history                                                                       Yes                 No
Ability to move position with Change Job action                                              Yes                 Yes
Individual positions can be moved as part of a reorganization                                Yes                 Yes
Hiring limits enforced                                                                       Yes                 No
Security stays with the position vs. the person                                              Yes                 Configurable
Ability to use JOB Requistion functioanlity                                                  Yes                 Yes
